flowchart LR
    I[Intent proposed] --> A[Accepted for work]
    A --> W[Active implementation]
    W --> V[Verification]
    V --> R[Ready for release]
    R --> D[Deployment or rollout]
    D --> O[Observation]
    O --> S{Accepted outcome?}
    S -->|Yes| C[Completed]
    S -->|No| X[Rework, rollback, or abandon]
    X --> W
